              <h4 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#0d4d3e] mb-2">Isuzu D-MAX LS-U</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-lato font-light text-sm">~$55,000 driveaway → ~$1,076/month</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
              <h4 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#0d4d3e] mb-2">Mazda BT-50 GT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-lato font-light text-sm">~$56,000 driveaway → ~$1,096/month</p>
